<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-22-0304 </DOCNO><TEXT>CoalCorp was formed from the operations of State Coal Mines, a divisionof the Ministry of Energy on 1 April 1987 and is a major producer, exporterand marketer of coal. The Corporation was one of nine newly created state-ownedenterprises. All the assets of the Corporation are owned by the shareholders- the Ministers of Finance, and State Owned Enterprises, on behalf ofthe Crown. Since its formation, CoalCorp has refocussed the production,orientation and political accountability of State Coal Mines, with theobjective of the becoming market driven and private sector oriented inall aspects of its business.</TEXT></DOC>